name: Bunny Jump: Love & Play 5
description:
Use the arrow keys to navigate this exciting map that is a tree.

Happy Bunny Friends is a team of five people who made this game at Game Jam in Skellefteå, Sweden.

The team consists of three artists:

Ann-Christine Troberg, Henna Hissa and Texas Olsson.

And two programmers:

Lukas Lindberg and Simon Stensmar.
